                <name>Zoë C.</name>
            </author>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[This is done for a friend who wanted to know more about the Chinese myths in which the Earth was severed from Heaven. I translated three excerpts where this myth was attested, with the original texts attached.
I hesitated about where to put this post, and decided against placing it under the section “Translations”, because it would have read out-of-place alongside the literary works.]]></summary>
